   The MgH distance was kept fixed at its experimental equilibrium distance
   in the X(2)Sigma ground state. The ab initio calculated interaction
   energies of the two PESs were. fitted analytically on the basis of
   Legendre polynomials for future collisional rotational excitation study.
   The (1)A' and (3)A' adiabats both present very deep well corresponding
