   rotation spectra, and spectroscopic constants were determined for the
   v=0 to 4 levels of (MgH)-Mg-24 and the v=0 to 5 levels of (MgD)-Mg-24.
   In addition, Dunham constants and Born-Oppenheimer breakdown correction
   parameters were obtained in a combined fit of the six isotopomers. The
   equilibrium vibrational constants (omega(e)) for (MgH)-Mg-24 and
   (MgD)-Mg-24 were found to be 1492.776(7) cm(-1) and 1077.298(5) cm(-1),
